 with 10/10 PASS. `codeharness verify` passed immediately.\n\nIssue: `state set` command did not persist reliably — had to re-run it for 14-6. The `state set` writes to sprint-state.json but the derived YAML is only regenerated by certain commands (writeStateAtomic), not by `state set`.\n\n### 14-4-observability-backend-choice — verify (2026-03-27T06:26:00Z)\n\nUnit-testable verification via subagent. ALL_PASS (10/10 ACs).\n\n## Token Report (14-4 subagent)\n- Total tool calls: 20\n- By tool: Bash: 7, Read: 3, Grep: 13, Write: 2\n- Largest Bash outputs: `npx vitest run` (~30 lines), grep remote-direct (~100+ lines), `wc -l` (~10 lines)\n- Files read: 3 unique, 3 total reads\n- Redundant operations: First Write of proof wasted (wrong format, had to rewrite). Broad grep for remote-direct across all src/ was excessive.\n\n### 16-1-verification-tier-type-and-utilities — dev (2026-03-27T06:42:00Z)\n\nNo issues reported. All 9 ACs implemented, 3842 tests pass.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 22\n- By tool: Bash: 5, Read: 6, Edit: 9, Grep: 7, Glob: 2, Write: 1\n- Largest Bash outputs: full test suite (~20 lines), verify module tests (~6 lines), vitest re-run (~15 lines)\n- Files read: 8 unique, 9 total reads\n- Redundant operations: none\n","structuredPatch":[{"oldStart":33,"oldLines":3,"newStart":33,"newLines":18,"lines":[" - Largest Bash outputs: full test suite (~20 lines), verify module tests (~6 lines), vitest re-run (~15 lines)"," - Files read: 8 unique, 9 total reads"," - Redundant operations: none","+","+### 16-1-verification-tier-type-and-utilities — review (2026-03-27T06:52:00Z)","+","+- HIGH: Parser tests had zero tier field coverage — tier derivation logic was untested (fixed)","+- MEDIUM: `VERIFICATION_TAG_PATTERN` regex rejected new tier values — new tags silently ignored (fixed)","+- MEDIUM: `parseVerificationTag` return type couldn't express new tier values (fixed)","+- LOW (not fixed): `runtime-provable` tier unreachable via heuristic classification (deferred to 16-2)","+- LOW (not fixed): `VerificationStrategy` deprecation message misleading","+","+## Token Report","+- Total tool calls: 22","+- By tool: Bash: 7, Read: 9, Edit: 7, Grep: 6, Glob: 2, Skill: 1","+- Largest Bash outputs: `npx vitest run` (~50 lines x2), `git diff --stat` (~12 lines)","+- Files read: 12 unique, 13 total reads","+- Redundant operations: none"]}],"userModified":false,"replaceAll":false}}
